it.polito.dp2.RNS

Interface PlaceReader

  • All Superinterfaces:
    IdentifiedEntityReader
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    GateReader, ParkingAreaReader, RoadSegmentReader

    public interface PlaceReader
extends IdentifiedEntityReader
    An interface for reading information about a place in the RNS system. In addition to the unique id, inherited from IdentifiedEntityReader, a place is also characterized by its capacity, i.e. the maximum number of vehicles it should be able to contain. It can be connected to other places.
